     98          /**
     99           *  @brief      It initializes the BackgroundThread module and its variables
    100           *  @details    Initialize method checks if BackgroundThreads_Stack_Area can contain all stacks defined in
    101           *              BACKGROUNDTHREADS_STACK_LIST macro before creating all Background threads.
    102           *              Checks if embOS supports Round Robin feature to perform Background threads switch;
    103           *              if not only one thread will be allowed to be defined.
    104           *
    105           *              If one of these checks fail no threads will be created: Run and ReserveThread methods will return FAIL.
    106           *
    107           */

